<p class="p" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">各设区市教育局，有关高校：</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">根据教育部有关高职单招工作要求，结合我省实际，制定了《江西省</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">2023年高等职业教育单独招生实施办法》，现印发给你们，请认真遵照执行。</span></span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">2023年实施高职单独招生高校（以下简称“单招高校”）要成立校领导任组长，招生、教务、纪检监察、后勤、卫生防疫、安全保卫等有关部门负责同志为成员的高职单招工作领导小组，建立健全监督机制，确保高职单招考试录取工作公平、公正、公开。要进一步完善招生考试工作应急预案，快速、妥善处置突发事件，确保考试招生安全、有序实施。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">2023年高职单招网报期间，考生自行登录江西省教育考试院“高职单招报考系统”，统一报考院校及专业。各市、县（区）教育局、教育考试机构要积极做好高职单招政策及实施方案宣传解读工作，确保2023年全省高职单招工作顺利进行。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:right;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">江西省教育厅</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:right;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">2023年1月8日</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span class="15" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12.5pt; font-family: 黑体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">江西省</span>2023年高等职业教育单独招生实施办法</span></strong></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">根据教育部有关高职单招工作要求，结合我省实际，现制定《江西省</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">2023年高等职业教育单独招生实施办法》（以下简称《单招办法》）。</span></span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span class="15" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">一、招生原则</span></strong></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">2023年高等职业教育单独招生工作（以下简称“高职单招”）坚持公平、公正、公开原则，由省教育厅有关部门统筹规划，单招高校组织实施，省教育考试院进行考试录取监督，确保我省高职单招的各项工作管理严格，规范有序。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span class="15" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">二、招生高校</span></strong></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">经省教育厅批准</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">2023年开展高职单独招生的高校（名单将另行发布）。</span></span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span class="15" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">三、招生对象</span></strong></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">已完成江西省</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">2023年普通高考报名的考生均可报考。尚未完成高考报名的，可于3月1-3日到户籍或毕业学校所在县（市、区）教育考试中心办理补报名手续。</span></span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span class="15" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">四、招生简章</span></strong></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">各单招高校应根据教育部及省教育厅有关高等职业教育单独招生工作规定，按照本《单招办法》要求，结合自身办学实际，研究制定</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">2023年高职单招简章（包括考试办法、单招专业、单招计划数、录取规则等）并向社会公布。</span></span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span class="15" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">五、考生报考</span></strong></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">1.网上报考：3月7日9:00—9日17:00期间，考生自行登录江西省教育考试院网（网址：www.jxeea.cn）“高职单招报考系统”，签订《江西省2023年高职单招考生诚信报考承诺书》（见附件1，承诺高职单招录取后不再参加2023年6月举行的统一高考），每个考生限报1所高校，可选不超过5个专业及是否服从专业调剂。在规定的网报时间内，考生可以对所报考院校及专业修改1次。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">2.数据下载：单招高校于3月11—12日前在“江西省普通高校高职单招管理系统”下载报考本校考生数据。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">3.考试确认：考生须按照报考高校的要求按时到现场或网上确认参加考试，领取或下载准考证。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span class="15" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">六、考试工作</span></strong></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">高职单招考试由单招高校组织实施，以</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">“文化素质+职业技能（或职业适应性）”测试为主，可以开展多校联合命题、联合考试，在确保安全、公平的前提下可以采用线上测试。</span></span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">1.考试要求：单招高校应组建命题专家组，科学、合理设计考试内容和评分标准，采取“文化素质+职业技能”的考试评价方式，总分满分为450分（文化素质部分占比不超过50%）。其中，文化素质考试科目为语文、数学。职业技能或职业适应性测试可以根据招生专业的培养要求进行设计。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">2.考试时间：在3月底前，由各单招高校根据实际情况自行安排考试时间并通知考生。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">3.考试纪律：严格执行国家教育考试考务管理的规定及要求，监考人员要认真查验考生身份，严格考务管理、严肃考场纪律、加强诚信教育。加大巡查力度，切实维护高职单招的考试环境和良好的考试秩序。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">采用线上考试的高校，一要做好线上考试系统安全性、稳定性的全面测试；二要加强线上监考人员培训，包括处置各类偶发、突发情况应急培训；三要给每一位考生提供不少于</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">2次的线上测试演练；四要优化系统功能，通过人脸识别逐一验证考生身份，强化监考,严防各种线上考试舞弊行为；五要对考试过程进行全程录像备查。</span></span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">4.考试成绩：单招高校要严格按照教育部和省教育厅有关评卷工作管理要求，切实做好评卷组织、管理、质量监控和安全保密工作。评卷、统分结束后，应及时在本校网站上提供考生成绩查询，并制订考生成绩复核办法及程序，为考生提供成绩复核服务。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span class="15" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">七、录取工作</span></strong></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">（一）录取原则</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">单招高校应合理确定文化素质和技能测试分数的录取控制线，按照简章向社会公布的招生专业、招生计划数及录取规则择优录取考生。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">高职单招录取严格执行省教育厅下达各校的单招计划和单招专业，不得违规突破。考生在录取后不得退录。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">（二）优惠政策</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">高职单招录取执行普通高校招生录取相关优惠政策。具体见《江西省关于进一步深化高考加分改革的实施方案》（赣招委字〔</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">2019〕25号）。</span></span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">（三）录取安排</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">1.4月5日前，单招院校确定拟录取考生名单并在本校网站进行公示。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">2.4月9日前，单招院校将录取数据库上传至“江西省普通高校高职单招管理系统”。4月10—11日持录取数据库（光盘）到省教育考试院审核备案并办理录取手续。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">3.4月15日前，单招院校在本校网站公布正式录取的考生名单，寄发本校印制的录取通知书。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">（四）录取说明</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">1.通过高职单招录取的考生，与参加统一高考录取的考生享受相同待遇。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">2.高职单招录取的考生须参加所在县（区）考试中心统一组织的高考体检。新生入校后，高校可依据教育部、卫生部、中国残疾人联合会印发的《普通高等学校招生体检工作指导意见》和人力资源社会保障部、教育部、卫生部《关于进一步规范入学和就业体检项目维护乙肝表面抗原携带者入学和就业权利的通知》等有关要求以及学校招生章程中对身体条件的具体规定，对高考体检或新生入学复检结论涉及限报的单招考生可进行调整专业以及退学、休学等处理。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">3.考生经高职单招录取后，不再具有参加统一高考及录取资格。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span class="15" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">八、工作要求</span></strong></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">（一）加强组织领导</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">各单招高校要认真履行主体责任，主要负责同志是第一责任人。学校成立工作领导小组，切实落实好各项职责分工。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">1.完善考试安全方案。单招高校要召开单招工作领导小组会议，认真研究制定考试安全工作方案。要按照国家教育考试安全保密工作要求，细化完善考试安全保密、命题制卷、考试组织、评卷统分、监督管理等办法，工作方案既要符合属地防疫要求，又要确保考试安全和公平。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">2.认真落实防疫要求。单招高校按照属地卫健部门要求做好防疫组考工作，指导考生做好个人防护，不聚会、不聚集。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">3.严格规范考试管理。各招生高校无论是采用线上、线下、分设考点或校际联合考试等方式，都要严格执行有关招生考试管理规定，切实加强命题、测试、评分、统分、成绩发布等各环节安全保密和规范操作，强化过程记录，采用录音录像等手段，做到每个环节都备案可查，确保单招考试全过程规范有序、公平公正。</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">（二）加强宣传服务</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">各地各高校要统筹运用各类新媒体特别是政务新媒体，采取多种形式，精心做好宣传解读和咨询服务工作。各单招高校要及时、准确解读本校高职单招工作方案；要向社会公布咨询服务电话，并安排专人值守，畅通考生咨询通道，加强对考生报考、备考、防疫等指导和咨询服务。各市、县（区）招生考试机构要及时做好有关信息发布工作，方便考生查阅。各高中学校要通过召开班级会，利用微信群、</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">QQ群推送信息等形式，向家长和考生深入宣传高职单招政策和工作安排。</span></span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">（三）严肃招生纪律</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">各单招高校要严肃工作纪律，严格遵守高校招生</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">“十严格”“30个不得”“八项基本要求”等规定，切实按照《关于进一步规范我省普通高等学校招生工作严肃招生纪律的通知》（赣招委字〔2017〕9号）要求，严厉打击虚假宣传、有偿招生、买卖生源、委托中介机构招生等违规行为。对高职单招考试中违规的考生、高校及有关人员，严格按照《国家教育考试违规处理办法》（教育部令第33号）和《普通高等学校招生违规行为处理暂行办法》（教育部令第36号）等有关规定严肃查处。涉嫌犯罪的，移送司法机关追究法律责任。</span></span></p><p class="p" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 19.2pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75);">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); letter-spacing: 0pt; background-image: initial; background-p