moothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 21pt;"><a href="http://www.jxeea.cn/module/download/downfile.jsp?classid=0&showname%20=undefined&filename=885936e610744d038e22ef12eb6c5db4.pdf" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 0.3s ease-in 0s;"><img src="/resource/js/ueditor-1.4.3.3/themes/default/images/spacer.gif" width="16" height="16" style="background:url(/resource/js/ueditor-1.4.3.3/themes/default/images/word.gif) no-repeat center center;border:1px solid #ddd" word_img="file:///C:/Users/%E7%8E%8B%E6%80%A1%E7%90%B4/AppData/Local/Temp/ksohtml11968/wps2.jpg"/><span class="16" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(86, 64, 89);">2.江西省2023年高职单招工作主要节点流程图.pdf</span></span></a></p><p class="p" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 0pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 19.2pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 9.5pt; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75);">&nbsp;</span></p><p class="p" style="text-align:right;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 26.4pt 0pt 6pt; padding: 0pt; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 21pt; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">江西省教育厅</span></p><p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: rgb(75, 75, 75); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><br/></span></p><p><br/></p>